LanguageData.Miho_Elegans_Hediff.description: The Misty Flower Organ, or Elegans, is an organ that only exists inside Miho's body. It activates the water-soluble mechanites and spreads them throughout the body. One of the reasons it is called the Misty Flower Organ is that the tubes spread throughout the body resemble the stems of misty flowers.\n\nTo maintain the Misty Flower Organ, mechanites must be supplied periodically through the Helianto.
